<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><lyrics>[V1]
 1. Chawlhni Lalpa ei hun ngai tha'n,
 Na In ah ka leng ui Na ni'n;
 Gamgaw apata la hung gi,
 Thilpiek gimlim bangin pawmin.

[V2]
 2. Lei chawlhni hi bawn ka lawp ui,
 Vanah chawlhna nuomzaw a um;
 Ka sepgimnau hi a beih tieng,
 Kipak leh lawpin chawl ta'ng kau.

[V3]
 3. Buoina, lungkhamna bei ta'n a,
 Gitloh, gawtmun um ta puo'n a;
 Lungkham leh tauna bei ta'n a,
 Kumsawt in chawihat la sai tiu.

[V4]
 4. Ziechun gal lauh a um ta puoi,
 Chawlhdamna nuom chuh hi ta'n a;
 Zan lungkham buoina bei ta'n a,
 Kumsawt in khuo vak zing ta'n a.

[V5]
 5. Ngaklah um sunni, hung suok in,
 Gitloh, lungkhamna salhvak in;
 Dahna gam ka pelh tieng uleh,
 Pathien kawm achun chawl ta'ng kau.</lyrics>
<title>LORD OFTHE SABBATH</title>
<hymn_number>425</hymn_number>
</song>